♪

1647
01:22:21,153 --> 01:22:25,201
-So, now you're a fan
of the mistletoe, eh?

1648
01:22:25,331 --> 01:22:27,943
-Christmas traditions
have their advantages.

1649
01:22:28,073 --> 01:22:30,771
Especially when you
need to make a truce.

1650
01:22:30,902 --> 01:22:32,382
Or other things.

1651
01:22:32,512 --> 01:22:40,512
♪

1652
